                        "name": "bkarwin",
                        "displayName": "Bill Karwin",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I took a look at this proposed method, and tried to use it in both Zend_Db::factory() and Zend_Filter_Input::_getFilterOrValidator().  This idea needs to be explored more fully with respect to these use cases.  There is no solution to declare the superclass or interface that the loaded class must implement.\n\nThis idea needs to be proposed in our proposal process, and show use cases and how the solution can be used to satisfy those use cases.",
